349
00:18:21,020 --> 00:18:25,610
We were with Ogi-Yahagi and ordered some food to be delivered to our agency.

350
00:18:25,610 --> 00:18:30,080
We wanted lunch, but couldn't be bothered going out for it, so go it delivered.

351
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:35,920
We got Suzuki to call them, and told him to order the curry and whatnot that Ogi and Yahagi wanted.

352
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:39,390
So Suzuki went off and called a place and said,

353
00:18:39,390 --> 00:18:43,630
"Hello. Mr. Ogi wants curry, and Mr. Yahagi wants a katsu lunch box and..."

354
00:18:43,630 --> 00:18:46,910
